# vim: syn=perl

=head1 NAME

COADD_JSA_TILES - co-add JSA tiles together by tile number

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe takes a set of JSA tiles and groups them by
tile number.  It then co-adds the tiles for each tile.

